        "release_date": "1980-01-01T00:00:00.000Z",
        "description": "Step into a groundbreaking Quranic experience with our VR app on Oculus! Embrace the timeless ritual of page-flipping, seamlessly navigate Surahs, physical-like paging, and bookmark pages for a personalized journey. Tailor your exploration with number-based page navigation and zoom features. Connect intimately with the text using hand-tracking and intelligent face following. Enjoy adjustable screens and user-friendly navigation suitable for learners and experts. Immerse yourself further with a mixed-reality tea table, creating a serene backdrop for your spiritual quest. Elevate your Holy Quran exploration today, uniting tradition with cutting-edge technology. Download now on Oculus for an immersive and accessible experience.",
